This file outlines known bugs, planned features, and tracks progress on current development

v0.2.3: UnitLoader
 4: Use command (usable items)
 5: After each command something might drift away (exception is view command and any system command)
 6: Inventory command (open inventory, can use 'inv') inventory is a whole other GameState
 7: Use and equip commands
 8: Player unlockables (condition trait for each unlockable)
 9: Achievements (check after each command)
 10: Level up
 11: Tier up (go to next chapter)
 12: Combatable trait extends Damagable (impl for Player and Unit)
 13: Environment features (which are Damagable)
 14: Turn-based combat
 15: Quests (check after each command) has condition trait (like achievement)
 16: Currency for shops (can purchase is a condition trait)
 17: Have secondary currency which is used to unlock player unlockables

